<!-- Product Section -->
 <section id="product" class="product-section">
  <div class="container">
   <div class="row">
    <div class="col-lg-12">
     	<h1>Products</h1>
	</div>
	<div class='satmass'>
		<strong>SatMass&trade;</strong>
	</div>
   </div>
   <div class="row">
	<div class="col-lg-8">
		<p><img src="../public/img/screen_main.png" class="screen-main"></p>
	</div>
	<div class="col-md-4">
	 <div class="scroll-text">
	    	<p data-sr='vFactor 0.6'>Created by a mechanical engineer with a background in spacecraft development, SatMass&trade; is a tool for advanced mass properties management and analysis.</p>
			<p data-sr='vFactor 0.6'>SatMassTM enables a systems engineer or mass properties analyst to compile component-level mass information into a complete picture with accurate and rapid results. It's modeling approach and analytical tools make it applicable from the earliest trade studies and risk projections to detailed design and analysis.</p>
			<p data-sr='vFactor 0.6'>Developed with spacecraft, light aircraft, UAV's, and launch vehicles in mind, SatMassTM can handle all your technical and business needs.</p>
	 </div>
	</div>
   <div class="row">	
	<div class="col-lg-12">
	 <div class="scroll-text">			
		<p data-sr='vFactor 0.6'>In addition to tracking basic mass properties, SatMass&trade; offers principal inertia computation, 3D rendering of parts and assemblies, uncertainty modeling, an advanced balancing routine, and much more! See a detailed list of SatMass&trade; features.</p>
 		<p><a class="btn btn-default page-scroll" href="#about" role="button">Learn more about SatMass&trade;&raquo;</a></p>
	 </div>
 	</div>
   </div>
  </div>
 </section>

